---
title: Thyme Roasted Chicken and Gravy with Roast Potatoes, Creamed Greens and Mashed Swede
description: We love a good Chicken with Potatoes & Mashed Swede and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thyme-roasted-chicken-and-gravy-3ed3400a-6816c300.jpg
